alfredsnippet.snippet:
# create screen 			--> screen -S <name>
# go inside screen 		--> screen -r saal
# list screen 				--> screen -ls
# come out from screen 	--> ctrl + a + d
# close screen 			--> screen -X -S <name> quit
# close all screen 			--> screen -X quit
alfredsnippet.name: INFO screen command go inside
